description.en:
ZELWIN is a global goods marketplace that provides an online trading platform to combine efficient digital assets and e-commerce services. A competitive advantage that distinguishes Zelwin from Amazon or Alibaba is that customers get guaranteed cashback in ZLW tokens for purchases and these tokens can be exchanged with cryptocurrencies, USD/EUR, or transferred to a VISA or MasterCard.

The ready-made product includes a clear business model and mass adoption is targeted through a versatile Affiliate Program.
